# AI Development Rules for @ojiepermana/angular

## Project
Angular UI library with FLAT ARCHITECTURE using op- prefix.

## Structure
```
lib/
├── components/  # op-button, op-card
├── services/    # theme.service.ts
├── pipes/       # all pipes
├── directives/  # all directives
├── utils/       # utilities
└── types/       # types
```

## Rules
- Selector: op- prefix
- Class: Op prefix (OpButton)
- File: kebab-case
- Standalone components
- Signals + input()/output()
- Flat structure only
- Export via index.ts
- Update public-api.ts

## Forbidden
- /ui/component/ structure
- Nested folders
- NgModules
- Missing op- prefix
